%%diagra:theme dark
%%diagra:icons azure
%%diagra:animate flow
%%diagra:font Inter

flowchart LR
  %% API Management fronts the AI application and applies policy.
  Apps[AI Client Apps]:::generic-browser
  APIM[API Management]:::azure-apim
  Orchestrator[Functions Orchestrator]:::azure-functions

  %% Documents and chat history support retrieval augmented generation.
  Blob[Blob Storage Documents]:::azure-blobstorage
  Search[Azure AI Search]:::generic-database
  OpenAI[Azure OpenAI Service]:::generic-api
  Cosmos[Cosmos DB Chat History]:::azure-cosmosdb
  Monitor[Azure Monitor]:::azure-monitor

  Apps -->|Chat Request| APIM
  APIM -->|Authorized Request| Orchestrator
  Blob -->|Indexed Content| Search
  Orchestrator -->|Retrieve Context| Search
  Orchestrator -->|Prompt with Context| OpenAI
  Orchestrator -->|Store Conversation| Cosmos
  Orchestrator -.->|Telemetry| Monitor
  OpenAI -.->|Usage Metrics| Monitor
